<div id="pf52" class="pf w0 he" data-page-no="52"><div class="pc pc52 w0 he"><img class="bi x0 y0 w1 hf" alt="" src="bg52.png"/><div class="t m78b x2f h34 yea ff2 fs5 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Lesson 10 </div><div class="t m4 x30 h34 yeb ff2 fs5 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"></div><div class="t m80b x13 h34 yea ff2 fs5 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">November 27-December 3 </div><div class="t m31f x6b h43 y8df ff2 fs24 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Latter Rain </div><div class="t m1b x2f h3b y8e0 ff5 fs20 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Sabbath Afternoon </div><div class="t m504 x55 h27 y265 ff2 fs18 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">READ FOR THIS WEEK&apos;S STUDY: Hosea 6:3; Joel 2:15-32; </div><div class="t m80c x55 h27 y46d ff2 fs18 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Zech. 10:1; Luke 11:13; James 5:7-10. </div><div class="t m80d x23 h27 y8e1 ff2 fs18 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">MEMORY TEXT: &quot;Then shall we know, if we follow on to </div><div class="t m80d x23 h27 y8e2 ff2 fs18 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">know the Lord: his going forth is prepared as the morning; </div><div class="t m80e x23 h27 y8e3 ff2 fs18 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and he shall come unto us as the rain, as the latter and </div><div class="t m44e x23 h27 y8e4 ff2 fs18 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">former rain unto the earth&quot; (Hosea 6:3). </div><div class="t m80f x65 h27 y26a ff2 fs18 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">KEY THOUGHT: </div><div class="t m73d x77 h28 y26a ff3 fs18 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">An unlimited outpouring of the Holy Spirit </div><div class="t m810 x69 h28 y471 ff3 fs18 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">will attend the final proclamation of the three angels&apos; mes-</div><div class="t m726 x69 h28 y26c ff3 fs18 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">sages. The result will be an abundant harvest of souls ready for </div><div class="t m48f x55 h28 y8e5 ff3 fs18 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">translation into the kingdom of heaven. </div><div class="t m718 x65 h27 y562 ff2 fs18 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">THE GREATEST UNUSED POWER. </div><div class="t m811 x20 h28 y26f ff3 fs18 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Two people were ob-</div><div class="t m812 x69 h28 y270 ff3 fs18 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">serving Niagara Falls when one said to the other, &quot;This is the </div><div class="t m231 x69 h28 y564 ff3 fs18 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">greatest unused power in the world!&quot; </div><div class="t m352 x65 h28 y272 ff3 fs18 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Not so, my brother,&quot; came the reply. &quot;The greatest unused </div><div class="t m340 x69 h28 y566 ff3 fs18 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">power in the world is the Holy Spirit of the living God.&quot; (A. J. </div><div class="t m813 x69 h28 y567 ff3 fs18 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Gordon, adapted.) </div><div class="t m566 x65 h28 y477 ff3 fs18 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Holy Spirit will usher in the latter rain—God&apos;s enabling </div><div class="t m242 x69 h28 y478 ff3 fs18 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">power for the church to give its final proclamation of the ever-</div><div class="t m6f6 x69 h28 y88b ff3 fs18 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">lasting gospel. The latter rain will illuminate the church with </div><div class="t m814 x55 h28 y276 ff3 fs18 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the glory of God&apos;s character and will empower His people to </div><div class="t m815 x69 h28 y306 ff3 fs18 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">illuminate the world by bestowing upon it the necessary spir-</div><div class="t m770 x69 h28 y278 ff3 fs18 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">itual gifts and spiritual power. The latter rain ripens both the </div><div class="t m803 x69 h28 y8e6 ff3 fs18 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">church and the world for the final harvest in which Christ will </div><div class="t m816 x69 h28 y8e7 ff3 fs18 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;reap&quot; for His kingdom the souls seasoned in righteousness. </div><div class="t mf4 x69 h28 y8e8 ff3 fs18 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">82 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
